To build:
1. Configure ./src/main/resources/arkifier.properties
2. From this directory (arkifier/) issue "mvn package"
3. Copy ./target/arkifier-dist.tar.gz to wherever you'd like and unpack 
(tar xzvf arkifier-dist.tar.gz)

To use:
From wherever you unpacked the distribution, call the shell script 
(./arkify.sh) without any arguments or options to view help.

